item.title: 324 - The Roswell Incident
item.description: Today's podcast is about one of America's favorite conspiracy theories, The Roswell Incident. In 1947, debris was recovered from a ranch near Roswell, New Mexico that was recovered by personnel from the nearby Army Air Field. The stuff of conspiracy began when the Army announced it had picked up a "flying disc" before retracting the statement the next day.
